Package org.cpnsim.core

Class SimEntityNull

java.lang.Object
org.cpnsim.core.SimEntityNull
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<SimEntity>, Runnable, Identifiable, Nameable, SimEntity
public class SimEntityNull extends Object implements SimEntity
A base interface used internally to implement the Null Object Design Pattern for interfaces extending SimEntity. It's just used to avoid the boilerplate code in such Null Object implementations.
Author:
Manoel Campos da Silva Filho
